{"tid":2488730,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"aespa遭工作人員非法偷拍！6秒片「錄下超噁過程」網氣炸：太猖狂","createTime":"2021-04-14T12:10:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T12:29:51.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1e13d3793e66622e473be36abde128af7c16ff5e","tid":2488730,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:10:29.000Z","msg":"女團aespa是南韓最大造星工廠SM娛樂在2020年推出，出道前就掀起熱烈討論，出道後的成績也相當亮眼，成員們的一舉一動都受到關注。近日，有眼尖網友發現在團體拍攝雜誌畫報的幕後花絮中，有一名男性工作人員鬼鬼祟祟地疑似偷拍了成員Karina與Winter，短短6秒片段被剪下上傳到各大社群瘋傳，引發熱烈討論。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5565/d5565792.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5565%2Fd5565792.jpg&h=bc2ef93b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Karina與Winter疑似遭偷拍。（圖／翻攝aespa IG）<br />\n<br />\naespa的官方YouTube頻道在3月上傳了為時尚雜誌拍攝畫報的幕後花絮影片，其中Karina、Winter在拍攝中途接受訪問時，一名男性工作人員先是走到兩人身旁，拿出手機開啟了內建相機，接著若無其事地將鏡頭朝向2人，緩緩經過2人身後，在Winter背後時還將身體向下微傾斜，全程看起來疑似是在偷拍裙底風光，短短6秒的影片瞬間就在各大社群網站引起爭議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5565/5565788.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5565%2F5565788.jpg&h=e43148cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲一名男性工作人員疑似在拍攝現場偷拍Karina、Winter。（圖／翻攝YouTube／aespa）<br />\n<br />\n影片在推特上轉發破萬，「非法偷拍」關鍵字也登上南韓推特趨勢，網友看了相當憤怒，紛紛標記SM娛樂呼籲公司盡速處理，並留言寫下「鏡頭面前都敢這樣拍！那鏡頭之外呢&hellip;」、「這太囂張了」、「好噁心」、「太猖狂了吧？！我要吐了」、「這種光明正大犯罪的人一定要嚴懲」」、「心疼成員&hellip;這會成為陰影吧」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5565/d5565791.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5565%2Fd5565791.jpg&h=32a1fed8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲將影片速度調慢可清楚看見該工作人員打開相機。（圖／翻攝YouTube／aespa）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dnovLCb8lSQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdnovLCb8lSQ&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvgOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=b4180fc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dnovLCb8lSQ</a><br />\n<br />\n▲疑似偷拍片段。（影片取自YouTube，如遭刪除請見諒。）"},{"pid":"52e3dc62bc26077920abc6713562e01816283d3c","tid":2488730,"uid":294121,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:11:41.000Z","msg":"好想睇Karina對大奶奶<br />\n幾時有流出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d912e29b5de6e26f790ecfa3cef2b45bbe919379","tid":2488730,"uid":178660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:16:13.000Z","msg":"訪問緊都影咁猖狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d586dcec344083d929e5b098407f440b1a29eb90","tid":2488730,"uid":177639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:21:20.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 鏡頭前都咁"},{"pid":"09fddd732c90e2fb19d11384422f69132e36eea4","tid":2488730,"uid":110878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:29:51.000Z","msg":"有咩好影睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}